        <Badge variant='outline' className='capitalize'>
          {reportType?.label || row.getValue('type')}
        </Badge>
      )
    },
    enableSorting: true,
    enableHiding: true,
  },
  {
    accessorKey: 'status',
    header: ({ column }) => (
      <DataTableColumnHeader column={column} title='Status' />
    ),
    cell: ({ row }) => {
      const status = reportStatuses.find((s) => s.value === row.getValue('status'))

      return (

            statusValue === 'completed' ? 'default' :

          <Calendar className='h-4 w-4 text-muted-foreground' />
          <span>{range?.label || row.getValue('dateRange')}</span>

    enableSorting: true,
    enableHiding: true,

                {key.replace(/([A-Z])/g, ' $1').trim()}:

                {typeof value === 'number' ? value.toLocaleString() : value}
              </span>

          ))}

              size='sm'
              className='h-8 w-8 p-0'

              <span className='sr-only'>Download</span>
            </Button>
          )}
          <DataTableRowActions row={row} />

    },

      className: cn('sticky md:table-cell end-0 z-10 rounded-tr-[inherit]'),
    },

    enableHiding: false,
  },
]

  table,

              className='size-8'
              aria-label='Regenerate selected reports'
              title='Regenerate selected reports'

              <RefreshCw />
              <span className='sr-only'>Regenerate selected reports</span>
            </Button>
          </TooltipTrigger>
          <TooltipContent>
            <p>Regenerate selected reports</p>
          </TooltipContent>
        </Tooltip>

        <Tooltip>

            <Button

              onClick={() => setShowDeleteConfirm(true)}
              className='size-8'
